name: Jimmy Long
text: Offered generic info to pass out. Realy did nothing

name: Edwin Rudd
text: Always helpful in every situation.  Responsive to every request I have made to them.  Proud to be a Democrat and glad our party has this office and staff available to support our endeavors.  Thanks,  Ed

name: Jim McBride
text: Proud to be a Republican but the customer service there is terrible. They treat their donors like we owe them something.

name: Stephen Anderson
text: Have had to contact several times about general questions and voting policies. Very helpful, friendly and informative.
